{"id":7564,"date":"2012-10-03T15:42:06","date_gmt":"2012-10-03T19:42:06","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=7564"},"modified":"2023-05-18T11:29:39","modified_gmt":"2023-05-18T07:29:39","slug":"major-sins-idolatry-murder","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/major-sins-idolatry-murder\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sins: Major sins are idolatry, infanticide, adultery"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Mas&#8217;ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the greatest sin?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>To set up a partner alongside Allah, even though He alone created you<\/strong>.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>To kill your child, fearing he will eat with you<\/strong>.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>To commit adultery with the wife of your neighbor<\/strong>.\u201d Then, Allah confirmed the saying of the Prophet with the verse, \u201c<strong>Those who do not call upon another god besides Allah, nor kill a soul Allah has made sacred, except by right of justice, and do not commit adultery.<\/strong>\u201d (25:68)<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6001, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 86<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/i><\/b>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0630\u064e\u0651\u0646\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0638\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u